---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Skills & Tooling - Eric">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="page-container">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-ink">Skills & Tooling</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
          The tools and skills I actually use to get work done.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6">
        <article class="surface p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Engineering</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted">
            I build and maintain production systems, internal tools, and
            automation that support operations. I focus on reliability, data
            integrity, and clear ownership of services.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
            Languages and frameworks used in shipped work: C#, .NET, JavaScript.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="surface p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Data</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted">
            I design data models and reporting pipelines that turn GTM activity
            into trustworthy signals. The goal is decision-grade analytics, not
            vanity dashboards.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
            Stack: PostgreSQL, SQL analytics, ETL workflows, BI tooling.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="surface p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Operations</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted">
            I build operating cadences and execution models that keep teams on
            schedule. This includes SLA design, intake routing, risk tracking,
            and post-launch adoption.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
            Outputs: process maps, escalation playbooks, and KPIs.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="surface p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">GTM / RevOps</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted">
            I align marketing, sales, finance, and customer success around shared
            lifecycle definitions and clean handoffs. The focus is clear
            pipeline movement and consistent forecasting inputs.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
            Work includes lead-to-cash, lifecycle ops, and revenue signal flow.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="surface p-6">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Leadership</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-muted">
            I lead cross-functional teams with clarity and accountability. I
            keep communication executive-ready while staying close to the work.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
            Style: calm execution, direct ownership, and visible milestones.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
